Stop worrying about what supplements you should be taking or the newest fitness technology…

Focus on:

-Sleeping well
-Quality nutrition
-Proper hydration
-Training intensity

If these aren’t where they need to be, none of the extra stuff matters 🤷🏻‍♂️
Throwing an egg on a burger has become essential for me https://t.co/yGTm6zNt5g
